The paper also mentions metaheuristics, which is a subfield of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, and cs.DS, in that order.
